snippet.title: QuByte Classics: Thunderbolt Collection by PIKO - PlayStation 4 Gameplay
snippet.description:
As part of the QuByte Classics series in partnership with Piko Interactive, this compilation contains both Thunderbolt (NES) and Thunderbolt II (Mega Drive)

Thunderbolt, Thunderbolt II (C) Piko Interactive
QuByte Classics (C) QuByte Interactive
Also available on Xbox One and Switch
